oops 
class and object
object:collection of data and its functionality
class: blue print for objects
using the class we create objects
to create the class we need to use class

example program:
class person:
    pass
p=person()
print(p)

methods:these are function belong to class
define the method we use "def"
class person:
    def display(self):
        print("Heloo")
person1 = person()
person1.display()

FUNDAMENTAL FEATURES:
---->>Inheritance
---->>Encapsulation
---->>Polymorphism
INHERITANCE:
-->Base class = already existing class
-->derived class = newely derived class
